<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>渠道品类 on 短松江月</title><link>https://simons.qzz.io/tags/%E6%B8%A0%E9%81%93%E5%93%81%E7%B1%BB/</link><description>Recent content in 渠道品类 on 短松江月</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 29 Jan 2026 11:32:58 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://simons.qzz.io/tags/%E6%B8%A0%E9%81%93%E5%93%81%E7%B1%BB/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>品类三界之渠道品类（下）</title><link>https://simons.qzz.io/post/2025/04/channel_categories_in_the_three_categories_part_2/</link><pubDate>Sat, 12 Apr 2025 14:44:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://simons.qzz.io/post/2025/04/channel_categories_in_the_three_categories_part_2/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;这一篇继续讲《品类三界之渠道品类（上）》没讲完的部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="弱势渠道品类"&gt;弱势渠道品类&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在《品类三界之产品品类（下）》中讲到弱品类，通过品类自身完成心智预售的能力来判断是否属于弱品类。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;同样的渠道也有弱渠道。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;类似于弱品类的判断，通过分析消费者关注的是渠道本身还是渠道中的产品，来判断是否属于弱渠道。、&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;比如你需要一把螺丝刀，你会去杂货店或者五金店买，但是具体是什么店、叫什么名字，你并不关心，这样的渠道就是弱渠道。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>品类三界之渠道品类（上）</title><link>https://simons.qzz.io/post/2025/04/channel_categories_in_the_three_categories_part_1/</link><pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 08:45:01 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://simons.qzz.io/post/2025/04/channel_categories_in_the_three_categories_part_1/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;经过前文
&lt;a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/QLGnTaekzJi8BcOxO5r5DQ"
 
 
